# Autonomix Ignore File
# Uses .gitignore syntax. Files matching these patterns will be hidden from the AI.
# Edit this file to customize AI access to your project files.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Binary Unreal assets -- never send to AI (binary blobs, not human-readable)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
*.uasset
*.umap
*.pak
*.sig
*.ucas
*.utoc

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Build artifacts
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Binaries/
Intermediate/
DerivedDataCache/
Saved/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# IDE and solution files
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
.idea/
*.sln
*.suo
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.filters
*.vcxproj.user

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Package manager caches
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
.pnpm-store/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Large generated/cached data
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
ShaderCache/
*.bin
*.pdb
*.exp
*.lib
*.dll
*.exe
